{"tid":1685970,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"商務部：中美雙方經貿團隊牽頭人今日將再次通話","createTime":"2019-11-01T00:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T00:55:07.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"216c2d364848ce2be19d05ec3e36fccb60d7f49b","tid":1685970,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"商務部新聞發言人10月31日表示，中美雙方經貿團隊一直保持密切溝通，目前磋商工作進展順利。雙方將按原計劃繼續推進磋商等各項工作。雙方牽頭人將於本週五（11月1日）再次通話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e71df7a73b70e815ced6212037e376471f0f6a","tid":1685970,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:55:07.000Z","msg":"上年電話11月2千升"}]}